================================================================================
GRANITE GLOBAL TRAINING VALIDATION
================================================================================

This script will:
1. Train ONE global model on 15 diverse tracts (SVI 0.014-0.867)
2. Test on 10 separate holdout tracts (SVI 0.019-0.873)
3. Compare results to per-tract baseline
4. Generate comprehensive performance analysis

Estimated time:
  - First run: ~60-90 minutes (computing accessibility features)
  - Cached runs: ~10-15 minutes (training + validation only)

Press Ctrl+C to cancel, or wait 5 seconds to continue...

